Package: secubox-hexo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), python3-uvicorn | python3-pip
Recommends: docker.io | podman
Description: Hexo static blog generator management
 SecuBox module for managing Hexo static site generator via Docker.
 Provides blog creation, theme/plugin management, post editing,
 and deployment to various targets.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple blog management
  - Theme gallery and installation
  - Plugin management (sitemap, RSS, etc.)
  - Post editor with markdown preview
  - Preview server with live reload
  - Deploy to Git, rsync, SFTP
 .
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/hexo/ via Unix socket.
